<h2>Sore tongue, Soreness or burning inside of mouth and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms sore tongue, soreness or burning inside of mouth and white patches on tongue including Allergic reaction, Medication reaction or side-effect, and Thrush (infants and children).</p>
